data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in the Arbor Oaks Subdivision. Conveniently located near schools, park and Sportsplex. Home has stunning custom upgrades. Features include an open floor plan with a formal dining room and eat in kitchen. Large backyard with privacy fence and in-ground pool that will be perfect for entertaining. Call Brad Lindsey today for your private showing @ 731-414-2318.
